-and-file. Lynch=E2=80=99s first question: =E2=80=9CWhy do you still have a=
 job?=E2=80=9D Monahan=E2=80=99s answer, in part: =E2=80=9CLet me get to th=
e heart of the question you=E2=80=99re asking, because it=E2=80=99s a quest=
ion about leadership. When you=E2=80=99re fortunate enough to serve in the =
capacity that I serve, there are going to be criticisms.=E2=80=9D The whole=
 interview is
